#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Unit 11: CLI Argument & Environment Mapper
Parses the Claude Code CLI for process.argv and process.env patterns.
Outputs JSON maps for:
  - CLI argument patterns (argv-map)
  - Environment variable usage (env-map)
"""

